{"tid":860847,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[莫縮叔台] 泡菜恐怖 白色情人節：恐怖學校 (PC)","createTime":"2018-10-13T15:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T15:37:53.000Z","uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"67334746ff6f3ce6144ef455eef9c1aff522d93d","tid":860847,"uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:54:54.000Z","msg":"[莫縮叔台] 泡菜恐怖 白色情人節：恐怖學校 (PC)<br />\n<br />\n莫縮叔遊戲台<br />\n每個星期五、六、日晚上，<br />\n跟大家一邊傾計，一邊打機<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitch.tv/mokuncle/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fmokuncle%2F&d=MFJV4HSU9Pby1IFF45jfp%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=61da0b8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.twitch.tv/mokuncle/</a><br />\n<br />\n故事發生在2001年的韓國，玩家扮演一名名為李希民的轉學生，在白色情人節為了給他暗戀的韓小英一個驚喜而潛入學校。一旦進入後，希民馬上被困住並開始對抗種種超自然現象。在其他學生的援助下，希民橫貫建築物，躲避敵人並使用小道具揭開拼圖繼續前進，嘗試在黎明前逃出學校。<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/73/WhiteDay_Game_Title.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F73%2FWhiteDay_Game_Title.jpg&h=f59b020e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n========================<br />\n莫縮叔Facebook Page: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/MokUncle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMokUncle&d=MFJV4HSU9Pby1IFF45jfp%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=2c27757c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/MokUncle</a>"},{"pid":"1d199b02b8dcdf7f10116deffae7f9eaf5c8c130","tid":860847,"uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T15:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60bb1c601fad748e90d2aa73396df0e9556f567","tid":860847,"uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmo